Class VideoObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • teacheasy.data.PageObject
      • teacheasy.data.VideoObject

  • public class VideoObject
extends PageObject
    Encapsulates the data that describes a Video Object as defined in the TeachEasy digital lesson XML format. Extends the page object supertype.
    Version:
    1.0 13 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Alistair Jewers

        nXStart - Relative X axis start position (0 - 1).
        nYStart - Relative Y axis start position (0 - 1).
